One week ago, we weren’t just watching the news, we were the news! My nephew, whom I’ve been raising in my home, is a senior at Saugus High. The fear I felt dialing his number as I was told there had been a shooting is indescribable, a truly numbing experience. During the aftermath @saugus_cents has done a magnificent job offering therapeutic options. My nephew, @iqonicm has used his music to help heal.  This is such a personal take on his feelings and I’m so proud of his bravery to share it with others! Our children should not have to experience this, NO ONE should have to experience this. I’m in complete admiration for the strength I’ve witnessed firsthand! May God bless the victims, their families, and our community. #SaugusStrong #NeverAgain (link in bio for full song)
